                        <div id="page-title">
                            SCP-ES-114
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<div class="scp-image-block block-right" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://borradores-scp-es.wdfiles.com/local--files/collab:nico1/dado.jpg" style="width:300px;" alt="dado.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>SCP-ES-114-1和SCP-ES-114-2.</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>项目编号：</strong> SCP-ES-114</p>
<p><strong>项目分级：</strong> Safe</p>
<p><strong>特殊收容措施：</strong> SCP-ES-114被收容在站点-34的安全物品储存柜中。动用该物品需要三级以上安保权限。</p>
<p><strong>描述：</strong> SCP-ES-114是两个相关异常物品的合称，分别被标为 ”dado的抗压药“ (SCP-ES-114-1) 和”dado的降压药“(SCP-ES-114-2) 。</p>
<p>SCP-ES-114-1是156片不透明的金色药丸，被装在近似颜色的宽口瓶中。瓶身上贴了一张复印纸，写着”dado的抗压药“。服用该药片时，对象会出现突发的头部剧痛，呼吸困难以及伴随心悸的心率过速。上述症状会逐步加重, 约20分钟后，之前服下SCP-ES-114-1的对象会被一股未知的力量粉碎<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup>。</p>
<p>SCP-ES-114-2是33片药片，通体白色，存放在一个圆柱形的细口瓶中，外貌近似典型的药房中售卖的非处方药。SCP-114-2的标注方式近似SCP-ES-114-1，只是标签上写着”dado的降压药“。服下SCP-ES-114-2的对象报告其感受到恶心和头晕，并在约五分钟后突然冲向空中。在受控环境中的实验表明SCP-ES-114-2可以归零其服用者所受的重力，使其永远浮在空中。</p>
<p>SCP-ES-114-1和SCP-ES-114-2的效果可以通过相互服用来中和。</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+展示通讯</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-关闭</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>发现：</strong> SCP-ES-114-1和SCP-ES-114-2被发现于一通由驻智利圣地亚哥军事人员拨打的求助电话之后，通话声称有一个人”不用飞机就飞越了禁空区“。 基金会成员迅速展开行动，该男子(José Miguel de Marqués)被空运带走并逮捕。</p>
<p>在针对其公寓的搜查中，找到了SCP-ES-114及对象与'<span class="wiki-email">od.ad|odad#od.ad|odad</span>.'的电子邮件记录。邮件内容与SCP-ES-114的来源有关。</p>
<hr />
<blockquote>
<p>你好，<br />
我的名字是José Miguel，很高兴认识你。我是从朋友那里听说你的…据说你在这行相当不错。长话短说，我现在急需你的帮助。我想要点抗压的药。我感到走投无路。不管你要多少我都付你。<br />
拜托，请尽快回我。<br />
- JMM</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="border: 4mm ridge rgb(170, 50, 220, .6); 20px ##ff9900; background:#f2c2f2; padding:25px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><br />
你好</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">是的你信任dado给你最好的药<br />
我说150比索就好$$$$<br />
我给你链接你可以现在就付款好<br />
窝同意</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><a href="https://www.pagos4dadopls.da.do/pago?y=ahorasi150pesosgraciasmucho">https://www.pagos4dadopls.da.do/pago?y=ahorasi150pesosgraciasmucho</a></span></p>
<span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">- 你的好朋友dado 💊<br />
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><br /></span></div>
<blockquote>
<p>你好，<br />
- JMM</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="border: 4mm ridge rgb(170, 50, 220, .6); 20px ##ff9900; background:#f2c2f2; padding:25px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><br />
泥嚎</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">请查看一下你的电子邮箱</span></p>
<span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">-泥的嚎油dado 💊<br />
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><br /></span></div>
<blockquote>
<p>哦哦哦！<br />
你干活快得叫人难以置信。非常感谢。<br />
-JMM</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="border: 4mm ridge rgb(170, 50, 220, .6); 20px ##ff9900; background:#f2c2f2; padding:25px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><br />
dado有亚马逊prime会员</span></p>
<span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">- 拟的耗游dado 💊<br />
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><br /></span></div>
<blockquote>
<p>你好，<br />
我正在看包裹说明，这似乎是抗血压的药。我是想要能降低心理压力的药，不是要抗血压的。我很遗憾，这其中似乎有点误解。能给我换一下吗？谢了。<br />
-JMM</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="border: 4mm ridge rgb(170, 50, 220, .6); 20px ##ff9900; background:#f2c2f2; padding:25px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
<p><span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;"><br />
嗷<br />
窝肥肠抱歉<br />
dado敏白了泥是想要降低压力的药而不是压力的药，蒿的。<br />
请查看一下你的电子油箱<br />
我很抱歉</span></p>
<span style="font-family: Comic Sans MS;">- 你的朋友dado 💊<br />
<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/f5/Dancing_Zombie.gif" style="width:10%;" alt="Dancing_Zombie.gif" class="image" /><br /></span></div>
</div>
